Package venicehub

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleReader
    Receives input strings from console (transmitted by VeniceHub.java), converts them into TTE objects and put them into the TTEQueue.
    ConsoleWriter  
    DiskReader
    Reads data from disk.
    DiskWriter
    Writes compressed data to disk.
    IIOReader
    Listens to InstantIO namespace and receives data from slots.
    IIOWriter
    Writes data to InstantIO namespace.
    RPCServer
    Creates a RPCServer and receives commands, which are then forwarded to VeniceHub.
    RSBReader
    Reads data from RSB.
    RSBWriter
    Writes data to RSB scope.
    VeniceHub
    Contains main.
    VeniceReader
    Reads data from source.
    VeniceWriter
    Abstract class for writing data from TTEQueue to a target.
